[With this approval, we may see a clear difference in the number of cases
of pertussis once boosters in adolescents and adults come into use. How
long the booster in adults will protect for remains unclear. Only time
will tell whether the standard every-10-year booster in adults will be a
Tdap vaccine. - Mod.LL]
